  "title": "Service Delivery Manager [ SAP HR/HCM (ECC) ]",
  "description": "<p><strong>Mandatory</strong></p><ul><li>Able to clear national security clearance upon passing all interviews</li><li>Good track record in SAP HR/HCM (ECC) </li><li>Good track record in Service Delivery / Management for AO/AMS Projects</li></ul><p>Good to have but not a must</p><ul><li>AMS (Application Management Services) or AO/AMS project background. </li><li>Having additional SAP HR–related skills orexperience</li></ul><p><strong>Job Scope </strong></p><ul><li>Manage service delivery and operations for an SAP HR/HCM (ECC) AMS/AO project, ensuring stable system performance and service quality.</li><li>Act as the primary point of contact for service management, including SLA adherence, incident management, and continuous service improvement.</li><li>Coordinate with internal teams and stakeholders to ensure effective delivery of Application Management Services.</li><li>Bring strong hands-on experience in SAP HR/HCM (ECC), with preference for candidates from AMS or AO/AMS project environments.</li><li>Demonstrate solid understanding of service management processes in managed services engagements.</li><li>Additional SAP HR-related skills or functional experience will be an advantage.</li></ul>",
